welcome_message_body: Welcome to Kent, a charming city known for its historic architecture, beautiful parks, and vibrant arts scene. We invite you to explore all that Kent has to offer and to enjoy your time in this wonderful city.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport mainly serves Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights from select airlines.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport for up to 30 minutes.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport is a modern and spacious facility, serving both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport offers luxurious amenities and services for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available for free throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for general aviation and private aircraft.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the hub for all flights and passenger services.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free wifi throughout the terminal and waiting area.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bremerton Airport is used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the terminal building.
